data.description: Step into a world of modern elegance and timeless charm in this TURNKEY 5 bedroom 3 bathroom 3071sqft oasis, located in the prestigious Crowne Hill community where every corner whispers comfort and style! This perfect home is for the meticulous entertainer which features an open kitchen/great room design full of upgrades including granite counters, stunning wood flooring, beautiful white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and inviting fireplace!  The layout is very welcoming, complete with a DOWNSTAIRS BEDROOM and bath perfect for the in-laws or guests! Upstairs you will find the over-sized loft which makes for a great media area or ideal space for teens, billiards, crafts or executive office! There are also four more generously sized bedrooms, including a primary bedroom that offers a serene retreat with a spacious layout, a walk-in closet, an ensuite bathroom with luxurious amenities and a balcony that is perfect for enjoying the gorgeous view! The Backyard is the perfect size for entertaining, and even has a built-in fire pit for those cold nights! There is also a generous three-car garage, providing ample space for vehicle parking and storage! This is a must see! Close and convenient to top rated Temecula schools, wine country, excellent shopping centers, dining establishments, and recreational opportunities!
